name: FlightFinder AI
desc: An AI-powered flight search and trip planning application leveraging CrewAI, GPT-4o, and custom tools for seamless travel experiences.

name: DeepSeekR1 RAG
desc: A Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system utilizing Nvidia NIM DeepSeek R1 and FAISS for document-based Q&A with LLM-powered responses.

name: HF Text Summarizer
desc: An end-to-end NLP pipeline for text summarization using Hugging Face Transformers, following MLOps best practices with modular components and API integration.

name: LIM-Nutritionist
desc: An AI-powered nutrition analysis app using Google Gemini API to analyze food images and estimate caloric intake, built with Streamlit for a seamless user experience.

name: Multi-Language Invoice AI
desc: A Streamlit-based web application that uses Google's Gemini AI to analyze invoices in multiple languages, providing AI-generated insights and responses.

name: News Reporter AI
desc: An AI-powered news blog generator using CrewAI and Google Gemini API to research and generate tech blogs in Markdown format.

name: YouTube to Blog AI
desc: An AI-powered automation tool that extracts insights from YouTube videos and converts them into structured blog posts using CrewAI.

name: Multicloud Student Performance AI
desc: An end-to-end machine learning project predicting student math scores, deployed using AWS Elastic Beanstalk, AWS EC2, and Azure with Docker.

name: Network Security AI
desc: An end-to-end machine learning pipeline for network security, featuring automated ETL, threat detection, experiment tracking, and deployment with Docker and AWS.

name: Wine Quality Prediction AI
desc: An end-to-end machine learning pipeline for predicting wine quality, integrating DagsHub for version control and MLflow for experiment tracking.

name: YOLOv11 Streamlit App
desc: A Streamlit-based application for real-time object detection, segmentation, and pose estimation using YOLOv11, containerized with Docker and deployed via CI/CD.

name: Snowflake AQI Visualization
desc: An end-to-end solution for ingesting, processing, and visualizing Air Quality Index (AQI) data using Snowflake, Streamlit, and GitHub Actions for automation.

name: Book Genre Classifier
desc: A machine learning-based system using Flask to predict book genres from summaries, with text preprocessing and classification into multiple genres.

name: Fraud Monitoring Grafana
desc: A real-time fraud monitoring system for credit card transactions using Grafana for visualization and PostgreSQL on AWS RDS for secure data storage.

name: Image Watermarking App
desc: A Flask-based web application that allows users to add text and logo watermarks to images, with adjustable transparency and positioning, deployed on Heroku.
